A closer inspection reveals that most of the uncertainty is not experimental. Hybrid experiments in particular are able to make precise air shower measurements. An overview on these experiments is given in Sect. 2.5. The experimental uncertainty on the measured value of Nμ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
