				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$X_{\text{max}}$\end{document} that need to be further reduced, there are no such blatant discrepancies between the simulated and observed values of Xmax\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
