				\begin{document}$2~\text{EeV}$\end{document} (Abbasi et al. 2018b, 2021). A non-imaging optical array called NICHE (Bergman et al. 2020) is currently build, and the main array is upgraded to TA*4 to cover a four times larger area to gain more acceptance for energies above 50 EeV (Kido 2018).
