The NEVOD-DECOR experiment (Barbashina et al. 2000; Petrukhin 2015) is a single large 2000m3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
