				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$7~\text{TeV}$\end{document} by ALICE, CMS, and TOTEM. Measurements in p-Pb collisions are under study by CMS (Sosnov 2020) and would help to understand how diffractive dissociation is modified in an ion collision.
